      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白。所以起点是PatientRecords，通过Create Todo进入Created状态。那Created之后有哪些分支？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "HealthTech_PatientRecords",
        "Created",
        "Create Todo"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "Created可以启动工作进入InProgress，也可以直接取消。关键是Created内部要有子状态：先经过Draft，然后Finalize到ReadyToStart。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Created",
        "InProgress",
        "Cancelled",
        "Draft",
        "ReadyToStart",
        "Finalize"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "好的，Created包含Draft和ReadyToStart两个子状态，Finalize是转移条件。我注意到ReadyToStart结束后应该回到HIPAA_Vault？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Created",
        "Draft",
        "ReadyToStart",
        "Finalize",
        "HealthTech_HIPAA_Vault"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，ReadyToStart完成后数据要归档到HIPAA_Vault。现在看InProgress，它内部需要DiagnosticEngine介入，子状态是Started和InReview。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "InProgress",
        "HealthTech_DiagnosticEngine",
        "Started",
        "InReview"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "Started通过Submit for Review进入InReview，那InReview之后呢？Approve是回到PatientRecords吗？",
